Package org.biopax.validator.api.beans

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Validation.Identifier
    This is a generic functional object (strategy) interface that contain the only method, which is called by the validator framework to get an identifier or name of a model element to report an error about.

  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Behavior
    Validation rule behavior: IGNORE -- skip: do not validate, nor report any messages; ERROR -- report as error, fail if error limit is exceeded; WARNING -- report as warning.
    Category
    Categories of error
